
Welcome to use ReSizeable RAMDisk 2.03!

SRDISK is a virtual disk device driver and controller capable of using 
over 32M of XMS and/or EMS memory. The disk can be disabled and it's 
size can be changed without rebooting. It is shareware and a fee of 
US$12 is required for use beyond one month evaluation period.

See SRDISK.DOC for list of features, files etc.

